00:32:33,619 --> 00:32:34,660
Fine.

571
00:32:34,759 --> 00:32:36,729
Even if you give up on math,

572
00:32:36,730 --> 00:32:38,959
you need to bring up the grades of other subjects...

573
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:40,730
