574
00:32:41,430 --> 00:32:43,569
That's if you want to go to college for a decent life like you said.

575
00:32:45,339 --> 00:32:46,369
Okay.

576
00:32:47,140 --> 00:32:48,400
Take out your English textbook first.

577
00:33:16,799 --> 00:33:18,369
Why, you little...

