589
00:34:00,180 --> 00:34:01,240
Gosh.

590
00:34:01,740 --> 00:34:03,779
Here. Drink this.

591
00:34:03,950 --> 00:34:05,680
It's my favorite.

592
00:34:12,260 --> 00:34:13,289
Now go on and tell me.

593
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:16,158
You agreed to help me with my studies...

