00:34:18,429 --> 00:34:21,130
So go on and tell me, and I will do it.

596
00:34:22,099 --> 00:34:23,769
You really are sharp.

597
00:34:24,329 --> 00:34:26,339
You don't let anything slide, except for your grades.

598
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:27,400
Why, you...

