00:34:29,170 --> 00:34:32,579
I'm doing my best to think of what to choose.

600
00:34:34,309 --> 00:34:37,179
Sure, think about it and tell me.

601
00:34:39,380 --> 00:34:42,218
Oh, and I was always curious...

