00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:11,679
But if the assailant also sues the victim,

614
00:35:11,909 --> 00:35:13,019
then it could get messy.

615
00:35:14,119 --> 00:35:15,789
And there may not be proper punishment.

616
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:20,320
What kind of law protects the assailant?

617
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:25,059
Then what is the best punishment?

618
00:35:30,769 --> 00:35:31,829
Just kill him.

