638
00:36:47,110 --> 00:36:48,209
Is there anyone who wants to join me?

639
00:36:48,210 --> 00:36:49,609
- Me. - Me too.

640
00:36:49,610 --> 00:36:50,809
- Song Yi Heon. - Song Yi Heon.

641
00:36:50,980 --> 00:36:53,380
- Song Yi Heon. - Song Yi Heon.

642
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:56,488
By the way, do any of you like to play soccer?

643
00:36:56,489 --> 00:36:57,589
Are you good at soccer too?

644
00:36:57,590 --> 00:37:00,920
Hey. Compared to my soccer skills, my basketball skills are nothing.

645
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:03,828
Why have you been hiding your skills?

646
00:37:03,829 --> 00:37:05,460
We got beaten in soccer the other day.

647
00:37:06,860 --> 00:37:07,900
Hey, Se Kyung.

648
00:37:08,630 --> 00:37:10,099
We'll get our revenge, thanks to Yi Heon.

649
00:37:11,170 --> 00:37:12,170
That's good.

650
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:14,340
Yi Heon, you had been a loser hiding your real power.

651
00:37:14,769 --> 00:37:15,969
Why have you been hiding it?

652
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:18,610
Guys, let's play soccer during the lunch break.

653
00:37:18,769 --> 00:37:20,279
- Sure. - I love that idea.

654
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,780
- I'll buy you something to drink. - Seriously.

655
00:37:23,409 --> 00:37:24,949
Guys, sit down.

656
00:37:26,719 --> 00:37:28,179
I have your temporary report cards.

657
00:37:30,119 --> 00:37:31,119
The report card!

658
00:37:32,119 --> 00:37:34,689
(Don't throw away your report cards. Show it to your parents!)

659
00:37:34,690 --> 00:37:36,629
(Have a good weekend.)

660
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:38,760
Others called you a loser hiding his real power.

661
00:37:39,429 --> 00:37:40,760
But you're just a real loser when it comes to study.

662
00:37:42,269 --> 00:37:43,300
How dare you...

663
00:37:45,030 --> 00:37:47,940
For the first time in my life, I realized a variety of numbers...

664
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:50,269
could be on a report card, thanks to you.

665
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:55,510
Hey, all report cards are the same.

666
00:37:56,079 --> 00:37:58,110
Is the report card of a top student any different?

667
00:38:05,690 --> 00:38:06,719
Hey.

668
00:38:07,190 --> 00:38:09,429
It's as if this report card was written in a binary system.

669
00:38:11,030 --> 00:38:12,260
All I see is either a 0 or a 1.

670
00:38:13,300 --> 00:38:15,929
That's why you should stop dozing off and study harder.

671
00:38:27,309 --> 00:38:28,340
I can't go on like this.

672
00:38:28,840 --> 00:38:31,210
Let's grab a drink before heading to the study room.

673
00:38:48,460 --> 00:38:49,530
I knew it.

674
00:38:50,230 --> 00:38:51,469
