(Pineapple)

677
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:09,650
- Thank you. - Sure.

678
00:39:11,090 --> 00:39:13,489
I bought this for you and Yi Heon.

679
00:39:14,119 --> 00:39:16,789
You could've come empty-handed to your friend's house.

680
00:39:18,059 --> 00:39:19,059
Oh, no.

681
00:39:19,060 --> 00:39:21,230
It's a shame when you bought it for us.

682
00:39:22,199 --> 00:39:25,869
But Yi Heon can't have a fruit cake like this one.

683
00:39:26,369 --> 00:39:28,469
He's allergic to pineapple.

684
00:39:28,769 --> 00:39:32,639
His throat swells up with even the smallest piece of pineapple.

685
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:35,178
I heard he had a terrible incident when he was young.

686
00:39:35,179 --> 00:39:36,579
He almost died.

687
00:39:43,989 --> 00:39:45,150
Put it in the basket if you want it.

688
00:39:45,619 --> 00:39:46,719
Everything is on me today.

689
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:51,559
Hey, that's...

690
00:39:56,829 --> 00:39:58,199
Gosh. On days like this,

691
00:39:58,869 --> 00:40:00,069
I want to have soju...

692
00:40:00,070 --> 00:40:01,869
