693
00:40:03,769 --> 00:40:05,809
I want whiskey on the rocks with cheese too.

694
00:40:05,980 --> 00:40:08,610
Or chilled beer with dried snacks.

695
00:40:09,179 --> 00:40:10,980
You know about the drinks quite well.

696
00:40:11,809 --> 00:40:12,879
Did you drink often?

697
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:17,090
I'm just saying they might pair nicely.

698
00:40:18,190 --> 00:40:20,289
I think those are good food pairings.

699
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:29,429
You can have it if you want to.

700
00:40:34,469 --> 00:40:35,500
Have some.

701
00:40:36,869 --> 00:40:38,269
That's the favor I want to ask you.

702
00:40:40,309 --> 00:40:41,340
You want me...

703
00:40:42,610 --> 00:40:43,710
