704
00:40:45,050 --> 00:40:46,050
Yes.

705
00:41:08,170 --> 00:41:09,239
I knew it.

706
00:41:09,710 --> 00:41:12,070
Using that Do Anything card, isn't worth using on this cake, right?

707
00:41:13,679 --> 00:41:15,110
Is it all you could come up with...

708
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,579
after giving it deep thought?

709
00:41:25,250 --> 00:41:26,489
(Pudding)

710
00:41:26,789 --> 00:41:27,789
Hey.

711
00:41:29,530 --> 00:41:30,860
Is it okay for you to eat this?

712
00:41:32,260 --> 00:41:34,730
Why? Do you want to eat that too?

713
00:41:36,869 --> 00:41:39,099
Hey. My throat is...

714
00:41:40,639 --> 00:41:41,840
