715
00:41:46,909 --> 00:41:48,309
Hey, Yi Heon.

716
00:41:48,739 --> 00:41:50,179
Hey, get up.

717
00:41:50,309 --> 00:41:51,880
Are you all right? Yi Heon.

718
00:41:53,619 --> 00:41:54,619
Are you okay?

719
00:41:55,780 --> 00:41:56,789
Hey.

720
00:42:10,929 --> 00:42:12,429
The swelling has subsided.

721
00:42:13,969 --> 00:42:15,170
They said you can go home now.

722
00:42:19,010 --> 00:42:21,010
What is this all about?

723
00:42:22,309 --> 00:42:24,309
Yi Heon is allergic to pineapples.

724
00:42:27,420 --> 00:42:28,880
Were you trying to kill me?

725
00:42:29,250 --> 00:42:30,349
You ate it yourself.

726
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:35,889
If you are indeed Yi Heon suffering from memory loss,

727
00:42:36,059 --> 00:42:37,630
others would tell you about it.

728
00:42:38,389 --> 00:42:40,259
The housekeeper said that was the first thing...

729
00:42:40,260 --> 00:42:41,860
she was told when she started working at your place.

730
00:42:42,559 --> 00:42:45,030
That you shouldn't have pineapples. That it could kill you!

731
00:42:47,539 --> 00:42:49,199
Why did nobody tell you that this time?

732
00:42:51,110 --> 00:42:53,110
Because everyone thinks you're Song Yi Heon.

733
00:42:53,710 --> 00:42:56,309
Because what you said about memory loss is a lie!

734
00:43:01,179 --> 00:43:04,389
I don't know why the test result said you were Yi Heon.

735
00:43:08,289 --> 00:43:09,489
But you are not Yi Heon.

736
00:43:18,429 --> 00:43:19,869
Could you help me?

737
00:43:20,840 --> 00:43:22,300
I know you can help me.

738
00:43:23,469 --> 00:43:25,440
Why would I meddle in your business?

739
00:43:27,579 --> 00:43:29,449
Please help me.

740
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:32,510
I'm begging you.

741
00:43:35,650 --> 00:43:38,150
After sending Yi Heon away from my place,

742
00:43:41,019 --> 00:43:43,289
I couldn't sleep for days because of the anxiety and pain.

743
00:43:44,130 --> 00:43:47,360
I finally got his number and called, but he didn't pick up.

744
00:43:49,059 --> 00:43:51,170
When he even skipped classes over the vacation,

745
00:43:52,300 --> 00:43:53,400
I got more anxious.

746
00:43:55,340 --> 00:43:57,969
The teacher told us he couldn't come because he was sick.

747
00:43:59,380 --> 00:44:01,440
I wondered if he got hurt because of me.

748
00:44:03,409 --> 00:44:05,150
Or if something happened to him.

749
00:44:06,719 --> 00:44:08,250
I couldn't sit still.

750
00:44:09,920 --> 00:44:10,949
Sorry about that.

751
00:44:11,949 --> 00:44:13,019
I really didn't think...

752
00:44:14,320 --> 00:44:16,229
it was you at the bookstore.

753
00:44:16,230 --> 00:44:18,460
- "Song Yi Heon." - I'm here, ma'am.

754
00:44:18,829 --> 00:44:20,530
But since I met you in school...

755
00:44:21,460 --> 00:44:23,030
and realized you were not him,

756
00:44:23,699 --> 00:44:25,900
