757
00:44:29,670 --> 00:44:31,570
It really felt like I was going crazy.

758
00:44:34,340 --> 00:44:35,880
I am so scared...

759
00:44:38,409 --> 00:44:39,480
that he might be dead because of me.

760
00:44:43,719 --> 00:44:44,719
You.

761
00:44:45,820 --> 00:44:47,860
What did you do to Yi Heon?

762
00:44:49,059 --> 00:44:50,559
I didn't want to get hurt.

763
00:44:51,090 --> 00:44:52,488
Part of it is your fault.

764
00:44:52,489 --> 00:44:53,530
No.

765
00:44:54,130 --> 00:44:55,599
It's all your fault.

766
00:44:59,170 --> 00:45:01,369
So, I treated him more coldly and brutally.

767
00:45:04,940 --> 00:45:06,079
So, just kill him.

768
00:45:06,610 --> 00:45:08,909
It's the only choice you have to protect yourself.

769
00:45:26,599 --> 00:45:29,929
Are you saying you want to apologize to him?

770
00:45:31,570 --> 00:45:32,599
Okay.

771
00:45:33,239 --> 00:45:36,210
I'll make sure you'll meet him. You can apologize to him then.

772
00:45:38,710 --> 00:45:41,480
He'll be back. I'll make that happen.

773
00:45:45,380 --> 00:45:46,380
When will that be?

774
00:46:04,570 --> 00:46:05,670
Sometime in the future.

775
00:46:06,599 --> 00:46:08,940
He might return faster if you help me.

776
00:46:09,340 --> 00:46:12,979
Until then, you have to help me...

777
00:46:12,980 --> 00:46:14,780
so he can come back safely and live a proper life...

778
00:46:15,440 --> 00:46:16,579
after he comes back.

779
00:46:20,119 --> 00:46:21,179
Help me with studying.

780
00:46:21,719 --> 00:46:23,049
As I told you before,

781
00:46:23,050 --> 00:46:24,949
