785
00:46:38,730 --> 00:46:41,039
I'll do it. I'll help you.

786
00:46:42,039 --> 00:46:43,940
In return, you have to bring him back.

787
00:46:44,869 --> 00:46:45,940
Bring Song Yi Heon back.

788
00:46:48,179 --> 00:46:50,449
He's not dead. Don't worry.

789
00:46:50,710 --> 00:46:51,780
So,

790
00:46:52,750 --> 00:46:55,579
you should do your best to help me study.

791
00:46:57,989 --> 00:47:01,420
I might be worse at it than you think.

792
00:47:05,360 --> 00:47:06,400
I know.

