Focus on the subjects that require memorization.

798
00:47:40,099 --> 00:47:42,929
(Reading, Korean History, Physics, Earth Science, English, Math)

799
00:47:44,829 --> 00:47:45,969
Hey, Se Kyung.

800
00:47:51,869 --> 00:47:52,909
Which one?

801
00:47:53,380 --> 00:47:54,440
Which question?

802
00:47:54,710 --> 00:47:55,980
"In the figure below..."

803
00:48:11,030 --> 00:48:14,199
"Observatory."

804
00:48:15,960 --> 00:48:18,130
"Flight."

805
00:48:19,199 --> 00:48:21,940
"Flight."

806
00:48:22,599 --> 00:48:23,670
"Panic."

807
00:48:40,619 --> 00:48:42,119
He's in a good place now.

808
00:48:43,429 --> 00:48:44,489
I guess so.

809
00:48:48,530 --> 00:48:49,559
Yes. Okay.

810
00:48:51,400 --> 00:48:53,469
Boss, they're almost here.

811
00:48:55,400 --> 00:48:58,940
Why are those punks sitting there?

812
00:48:59,739 --> 00:49:01,079
They are kids from this neighborhood.

813
00:49:01,480 --> 00:49:04,578
They are sitting out there all day asking for a job.

814
00:49:04,579 --> 00:49:06,149
If so, they should have come earlier.

815
00:49:06,150 --> 00:49:08,718
I can't focus on my work at all because of them.

816
00:49:08,719 --> 00:49:11,050
Boss, didn't you say you were out of cigarettes?

817
00:49:11,150 --> 00:49:13,119
- I'll go and buy them. - Okay.

818
00:49:14,090 --> 00:49:15,360
Those punks.

819
00:49:15,559 --> 00:49:16,888
I told you not to stay here.

820
00:49:16,889 --> 00:49:18,559
Well, come here.

821
00:49:24,800 --> 00:49:26,070
A clear sky.

822
00:49:27,500 --> 00:49:28,670
I want to see it too.

823
00:49:29,300 --> 00:49:31,309
I told you not to sit around here.

824
00:49:31,409 --> 00:49:32,969
Look at the color of this punk's hair.

825
00:49:33,380 --> 00:49:34,579
Gosh.

826
00:49:38,179 --> 00:49:39,449
Should I ask him...

827
00:49:40,179 --> 00:49:42,420
- about Kim Deuk Pal? - Do you really intend to find him?

828
00:49:42,980 --> 00:49:45,150
That punk learned how to fight from him.

829
00:49:45,590 --> 00:49:46,860
So, I want to learn from him too.

830
00:49:47,960 --> 00:49:49,019
Do as you please.

831
00:49:50,760 --> 00:49:53,328
Who learned how to fight from Deuk Pal?

832
00:49:53,329 --> 00:49:54,500
- Hello, sir. - Hello, sir.

833
00:49:55,860 --> 00:49:57,869
There's a crazy guy in our class.

834
00:49:58,070 --> 00:50:01,238
He said he learned how to fight from Chilsung Gang's Kim Deuk Pal.

835
00:50:01,239 --> 00:50:02,400
It just can't be true.

836
00:50:03,769 --> 00:50:05,570
The Chilsung Gang doesn't exist anymore.

837
00:50:06,480 --> 00:50:08,880
When Deuk Pal was alive, he could be overly generous.

838
00:50:09,139 --> 00:50:10,710
I guess his path crossed with that kid too.

839
00:50:13,280 --> 00:50:15,619
- Which school do you go to? - Hansong High School.

840
00:50:15,719 --> 00:50:16,749
We're graduating soon.

841
00:50:16,750 --> 00:50:19,119
We'll join you after graduation, so please give us a job.

842
00:50:25,460 --> 00:50:27,129
At your school, is there someone named Song...

843
00:50:27,130 --> 00:50:29,730
What are you doing, you punks?

844
00:50:30,429 --> 00:50:31,500
Gosh.

845
00:50:31,800 --> 00:50:33,738
Why did you step out of the car?

846
00:50:33,739 --> 00:50:35,539
I was going to take care of them myself.

847
00:50:35,699 --> 00:50:38,238
Didn't I tell you not to come here?

848
00:50:38,239 --> 00:50:39,879
Is that so hard to understand?

849
00:50:39,880 --> 00:50:41,940
Is that so hard?

850
00:50:45,679 --> 00:50:46,679
They're here.

851
00:50:48,449 --> 00:50:49,519
Okay. Let's go.

852
00:50:50,989 --> 00:50:52,389
Don't come here. Okay?

853
00:51:06,940 --> 00:51:08,868
- I'm sorry, sir. - What is it?

854
00:51:08,869 --> 00:51:12,009
One of us got arrested by the police not long ago.

855
00:51:12,010 --> 00:51:13,409
What kind of nonsense are you talking about?

856
00:51:16,449 --> 00:51:18,948
Boss, what if I go with them?

857
00:51:18,949 --> 00:51:21,118
We just need one person in the van to guard it.

858
00:51:21,119 --> 00:51:23,819
You punk! The Kwangsoo Gang knows who you are.

859
00:51:23,820 --> 00:51:25,989
Are you going to take responsibility if something happens?

860
00:51:33,260 --> 00:51:35,960
Hey. The one in green. Come here.

861
00:51:37,699 --> 00:51:39,469
- Hurry. - Yes, sir.

862
00:51:42,300 --> 00:51:43,610
You guys do the work.

863
00:51:45,369 --> 00:51:46,980
Make him watch from the van.

864
00:51:50,650 --> 00:51:51,750
You're lucky today.

865
00:51:52,449 --> 00:51:53,480
Where are we going?

866
00:51:53,719 --> 00:51:54,849
Would you know even if I told you?

867
00:51:55,119 --> 00:51:56,420
We're going to go and make money.

868
00:51:58,989 --> 00:52:00,090
Get in.

869
00:52:00,659 --> 00:52:01,690
Hurry up and get in.

870
00:52:12,800 --> 00:52:15,538
Hey, which one is correct here?

871
00:52:15,539 --> 00:52:16,639
Is it "a" or "the?"

872
00:52:16,809 --> 00:52:19,010
Hey. We went over this yesterday.

873
00:52:19,670 --> 00:52:21,139
I know.

874
00:52:21,309 --> 00:52:23,210
But articles are so tricky.

875
00:52:23,349 --> 00:52:24,449
Darn it.

876
00:52:31,789 --> 00:52:32,820
It doesn't have a license plate.

877
00:53:02,250 --> 00:53:03,690
Excuse me.

878
00:53:05,590 --> 00:53:07,089
Why did you cancel the police report?

879
00:53:07,090 --> 00:53:09,419
We have to find out who did it and catch the perps.

880
00:53:09,420 --> 00:53:10,928
If the police get involved,

881
00:53:10,929 --> 00:53:12,859
Yi Heon's life will change drastically.

882
00:53:12,860 --> 00:53:15,900
That won't be good for Yi Heon at all.

883
00:53:16,300 --> 00:53:17,530
I'm sorry.

884
00:53:17,929 --> 00:53:20,098
I found out through a detective I know...

885
00:53:20,099 --> 00:53:22,969
that the police report had already been retracted.

886
00:53:23,539 --> 00:53:26,210
I promise to get everything straightened out.

887
00:53:26,440 --> 00:53:27,779
They come occasionally when we sit around...

888
00:53:27,780 --> 00:53:30,249
in front of Sinho Nightclub at Sinho Hotel downtown.

889
00:53:30,250 --> 00:53:31,849
They are gangsters!

890
00:53:32,480 --> 00:53:33,819
I know nothing...

891
00:53:33,820 --> 00:53:35,849
other than they are part of the Dongsoo Gang.

892
00:53:36,789 --> 00:53:37,789
Dong Soo.

